sequenceDiagram
    participant SVC as Service (Booking/Calendar/etc)
    participant NS as Notification Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant TG as Telegram Bot
    participant U as User/Channel/Group
    
    Note over SVC,U: TYPE 1: Single User Notification
    
    SVC->>NS: create_notification(<br/>  target_type="user",<br/>  target_value=telegram_id,<br/>  template="booking_confirmed"<br/>)
    NS->>DB: INSERT INTO notifications
    NS->>DB: INSERT INTO deliveries (user_id)
    NS-->>SVC: notification_id
    
    NS->>TG: send_message(chat_id=telegram_id)
    TG-->>U: Message delivered
    NS->>DB: UPDATE deliveries (status=sent)
    
    Note over SVC,U: TYPE 2: Channel Broadcast
    
    SVC->>NS: create_notification(<br/>  target_type="channel",<br/>  target_value=channel_id,<br/>  template="new_practice_alert"<br/>)
    NS->>DB: INSERT INTO notifications
    NS-->>SVC: notification_id
    
    NS->>TG: send_message(chat_id=channel_id)
    TG-->>U: Posted to channel
    NS->>DB: UPDATE notifications (status=sent)
    
    Note over SVC,U: TYPE 3: Group Announcement
    
    SVC->>NS: create_notification(<br/>  target_type="group",<br/>  target_value=group_id,<br/>  thread_id=topic_id (optional)<br/>)
    NS->>DB: INSERT INTO notifications
    NS-->>SVC: notification_id
    
    NS->>TG: send_message(<br/>  chat_id=group_id,<br/>  message_thread_id=topic_id<br/>)
    TG-->>U: Posted to group/thread
    NS->>DB: UPDATE notifications (status=sent)
    
    Note over SVC,U: TYPE 4: Broadcast to All Users
    
    SVC->>NS: create_notification(<br/>  target_type="all_users",<br/>  template="platform_announcement"<br/>)
    NS->>DB: INSERT INTO notifications
    NS->>DB: Get all active users
    
    loop For each user
        NS->>DB: INSERT INTO deliveries
    end
    
    NS-->>SVC: notification_id, queued for X users
    
    loop Process queue (batched)
        NS->>TG: send_message(chat_id)
        TG-->>U: Message delivered
        NS->>DB: UPDATE delivery (status=sent)
    end
